[[=]]
> Locked up in containment, no trouble around
> SCP-999 makes a sweet, soft, sound.
> The doctors were listening and left wondering why,
> He was singing a Christmas lullaby.
> 
> 682 is growling, he won't go away,
> But little 999, can keep him at bay.
> One little orange blob can help us to stay safe,
> Can make all the keters sit down and behave.
> 
> To all the Foundation's hardworking crew
> To all the anomalies and dead gods too,
> To all of the world in this joyous time,
> Please have a Merry Christmas, from 999.
[[/=]]

